data.text:
Origin Malawi Pro Colour is especially formulated for Malawi Haps and Peacocks.

Colour enhancing

High digestibility

Low pollution

Contains Spirulina, Pepper and Astaxanthine

Includes prebiotic fiber, Inuline and Probiotics

High levels of Vitamin C and Omega-3 fatty acids

We know just what your Haps and Peacocks need; this formulation has been designed to maximise your fish’s potential. Malawi Pro Colour is built on a strong foundation of ingredients that will bring vitality and health to your fish. We then add to that some proven colour enhancers that will take your fish to the next level.

Our food is scientifically formulated to improve digestion and nutrient uptake, which will result in increased growth, improved health, and less waste in your water column. We have the very best ingredients, minimal fillers and trademarked ingredients to ensure this happens.

Malawi Pro Colour contains a rich mix of multivitamins with a high level of stable Vitamin C to help your fish’s immune system fight and resist disease. It also provides essential amino acids, Omega-3 fatty acids, and antioxidants like astaxanthin.

Feed 2-3 times per day in small portions. Feed as much as the fish can eat in 2-3 minutes.

Composition:

Krill Meal, Squid Meal, Fish Meal, Spirulina, Astaxanthin, Algae, Pepper, lecithin, Yeast Wheatgerm, Maize starch, and Fish Oil

Pellet Size: 1.2-1.5mm

Analyses (%)

Protein 52%

Fat 8%

Crude fibre 1,9%

Ash 9%

Astaxanthin (mg/kg) 85

Vitamins added

Vitamin A (IE/kg) 24.997

Vitamin D (IE/kg) 2.432

Vitamin E (mg/kg) 280

Vitamin C (stable) (mg/kg) 700

The values of the nutrients and vitamins are from the time of writing. These values can vary due to natural variation in the ingredients.

We reserve the right to change our recipes. For the exact values, we refer to the label.
